lass=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T04:01:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78a4f6f7306c473f211aabfa7e742be837f9fdfc","tid":2410894,"uid":165596,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T04:02:03.000Z","msg":"Biden: Ok. I&rsquo;m a VP now<em><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></em>"},{"pid":"d2de294140b93714a893b5817e55a8109cb966b8","tid":2410894,"uid":364021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"998c7e0c378026e87e2fd5787faf8db270562b3b","tid":2410894,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T03:23:16.000Z","msg":"美國副總統賀錦麗（Kamala Harris）上任後罕見行總統之職，致電多國元首，引發外界關注。<br />\n<br />\n2月15日，賀錦麗與法國總統馬克龍（Emmanuel Macron）進行了通話。賀錦麗發推文說：「我們討論了COVID-19（中共病毒）、氣候變化、支持國內外民主、區域性挑戰。美國總統和我期待著與馬克龍總統合作，為我們兩國建立一個更美好的未來。」<br />\n<br />\n白宮在一份聲明中說，賀錦麗「表達了她對加強美法兩國間雙邊關係和振興跨大西洋聯盟的承諾。」<br />\n<br />\n她和馬克龍「一致認為，需要進行密切的雙邊和多邊合作，來應對COVID-19（中共病毒）、氣候變化，並在國內及世界各地支持民主。」<br />\n<br />\n聲明稱，兩人還討論了中東和非洲局勢，以及共同正視這些挑戰的必要性。但聲明中沒有提及總統拜登。<br />\n<br />\n在和馬克龍通話之前，賀錦麗已經和加拿大總理特魯多（Justin Trudeau）進行了通話。白宮表示，這是她作為副總統首次致電外國領導人。<br />\n<br />\n特魯多辦公室的一份聲明說：「總理祝賀副總統贏得了她的歷史性選舉。她深情地回憶了她在蒙特利爾（Montr&eacute;al）度過的歲月。」<br />\n<br />\n聲明還表示，賀錦麗和特魯多也討論了其它事項，包括對抗中共病毒疫情。<br />\n<br />\n賀錦麗在通話後的一份聲明中說：「我們討論了在多個問題上緊密合作的承諾，包括對抗COVID-19、應對氣候變化、以促進兩國復甦並創造就業的方式擴大我們的經濟夥伴關係。」<br />\n<br />\n賀錦麗罕見行總統之職 ，致電外國元首，引起輿論關注。外界認為，副總統致電外國國家元首非常罕見，前副總統邁克‧彭斯（Mike Pence）沒有與特魯多或馬克龍通過電話，儘管他曾多次親自拜訪外國國家元首。<br />\n<br />\n保守派媒體《國家脈動》（National Pulse）對此批評說：「新一屆政府成立僅幾個星期，副總統就與世界主要領導人聯繫，很怪異。」這些電話可能表明，賀錦麗比往屆副總統擁有更高的地位，特別是在外交政策方面。<br />\n<br />\n現年78歲的拜登是美國史上最年長的總統，外界認為，賀錦麗這位年輕的副總統可能將承擔更多的政務工作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ntdtv.com/assets/uploads/2021/02/GettyImages-1230989014-600x338.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ntdtv.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2FGettyImages-1230989014-600x338.jpg&h=36fd5d68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDrew Angerer/Getty Images<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2021/02/17/a103055938.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2021%2F02%2F17%2Fa103055938.html&d=2uuoLuAEMU6cBVSXjgSp%2BWCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=3bc91797\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2021/02/17/a103055938.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T04:02:48.000Z","msg":"they just talk"},{"pid":"cb25a15535e039035a70173d68092eedc446be09","tid":2410894,"uid":226515,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b6c237cdc769638bc161d486e5df7131322d52fa","tid":2410894,"uid":282637,"like":93,"dislike":0,"score":93,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T04:01:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V3BQQZL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV3BQQZL.jpg&h=9a346fa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wHbEKjN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwHbEKjN.gif&h=a4360e5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T04:05:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c972de7d65cf62945327f246baaf16011a045d61","tid":2410894,"uid":255637,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b6c237cdc769638bc161d486e5df7131322d52fa","tid":2410894,"uid":282637,"like":93,"dislike":0,"score":93,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T04:01:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V3BQQZL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV3BQQZL.jpg&h=9a346fa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wHbEKjN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%